    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "The if statement is a basic check if the user has supplied a password. In the case of an empty password, or the user didn't supply the password in the request the user is presented with a password prompt. It is possible to unlock the account by hitting enter without typing anything. This will unlock accounts with an empty password. Note, there was/is a problem with the password prompt. This is fixed in #1710\n\nRemoving the if checkout isn't possible since it will give problems on the http channel. It can probably be removed later when we have a reliable way of asking the user for sensitive information.\n",
